{
  "stem": "13141.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then there was-- and, and, and I was told that an organization by the name of Judische Auswandererstelle [SPEAKING GERMAN] was being created.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were looking for people-- for all kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I applied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, I, I knew I didn't have much of a chance because there were many people who were applying.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my advantage was in one of the summer vacations, my mother had sent me to learn how to type and how to take shorthand.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I became very good at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they gave me a test, which came out very good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was employed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That organization actually was created by German authorities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was created about a, a year-- no, less than a year, maybe six or eight months after the Crystal Night, after November 9, 1938.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was created in 1939 for the purpose to take-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to help Jews to comply with their different papers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lot of paperwork involved if you wanted to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You needed all kinds of permits from all kinds of German authorities, from the police department, from the [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You needed an authorization-- what you could take along and what you couldn't take along.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were laws.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to pay what they called a Reichsfluchsteuer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That means you had to pay a tax because you were fleeing from Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's why they called it Reichsfluchsteuer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all this-- we helped the people with-- to make the corresponding papers and to fill in the papers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked with the, the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I had the opportunity to go to these different German authorities twice or three times a week.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
